author: Barry K
title: Woman Stupidly Films Her Oral Sex Act In Courthouse
text:
Your Privacy Rights Canadian Customers 
In Florida news, a Jacksonville woman who was already in court facing drug-related charges filmed herself giving oral sex in Duval County Courthouse’s empty hallway, according to The New York Post . Filming yourself giving oral sex and then posting the footage to Twitter isn’t a very good idea in any situation, but especially not when you’re in the same building as someone who will decide whether or not you spend some future portion of your life in jail, and definitely not when you upload the video with the accompanying caption, “Just found a way to get out of trouble.” It’s just a really bad look all around.
